Creating Infrastructure Using Code - Definition

IAC can be divided in three categories :
 1. Infra Provisioning Tool
 2. Configuration Management Tool
 3. Server Templating Tool (Image Building Tool)

EXAMPLE:
Creating the EC2 instance,VPC,S3 are the examples of infrastructure provisiong. 
Installing necessary software inside the EC2 instance is the example of Configuration Management.
Creating the AMI(Image) for the future use and other people to use it we have server templating tool.

